    "title_en": "Combined KM3NeT/ARCA and ANTARES search for compact neutrino sources",
    "abstract_en": "High-energy neutrinos from point-like sources are searched in the combined dataset from ANTARES and the available KM3NeT/ARCA data. This analysis demonstrates the potential of combining data from these neutrino detectors using a binned likelihood approach.",
